summary: Issues related to the test

story:
    As a user I want to link related external issues so that I can
    easily find out what is covered by the test.

description:
    Relevant external issues, for example features or bugs covered
    by the test. Should be a ``string`` or a ``list of strings``
    containing URL of the issue in the external tracker.

example: |
    issue: https://github.com/psss/tmt/issues/207
    issue:
      - https://github.com/psss/tmt/issues/207
      - https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1

implemented: /tmt/base
